data.description: PRICE IMPROVED! MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING YOUR BEST OFFER!! This beautiful residence is situated in a newer San Jacinto neighborhood. Constructed in 2006, this 2,519-square-foot Home offers a seamless move-in experience. Open floor plan with extra high ceilings in the living room, an island kitchen, and a family room. There is an extra room on the main floor that can be used as a bedroom or an office. Real wood floor thought out of the second floor.  Nestled in a fantastic San Jacinto community, this spacious modern home includes a generously sized master bedroom with an attached master bath, complete with a soaking tub, separate walk-in shower, and a convenient Jack and Jill vanity. The walk-in closet provides ample storage space.  This residence offers an abundance of space, including a 3-car garage capable of accommodating various vehicle combinations. The driveway easily accommodates an RV or outdoor toys. The vast backyard is primed for your future plans, whether that involves a pool, outdoor kitchen, or patio cover.  Moreover, the home's location is a short distance from Belicia Park, where children can enjoy the playground. Don't miss this exceptional and rare opportunity that combines everything you need with the potential to build everything you desire.
